fel.cvut.af.model.input

Class Input

  • java.lang.Object
    • fel.cvut.af.model.input.Input
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    BasicOptionsInput, DateInput, EndpointOptionsInput, NumberInput, PasswordInput, TextFieldInput, TextInput

    @Entity
public abstract class Input
extends java.lang.Object
    The predecessor of all Inputs defines all common attributes.

    This class represents single input which can be rendered by client app. It's descendants defines type of input or value type.
